With({fItems: Filter(pbMenu_2.MenuData,Upper(menuKey)=Upper(pbMenu_2.MenuKey))}, 
    If(CountRows(fItems)=0, 
        [
            pbMenu_2.MissingMenuRecord
        ]
        , 
        ForAll(fItems As mi, 
            {            
                ItemKey: mi.ItemKey, 
                ItemDisplayName:  mi.ItemDisplayName, 
                ItemIconName: mi.ItemIconName, 
                ItemAppearance: mi.ItemAppearance, 
                ItemIconStyle: mi.ItemIconStyle, 
                ItemTooltip: mi.too, 
                ItemDisabled: mi.ItemDisabled
            }

        )
    )
)
